cc:Work.dc:title: Misc - PhoneHolder
cc:Work.dc:description:
Smartphone desk holder
This phone stand holds your phone between two tabs, with access to its bottom, in order to connect a charger, headphones, and also not to obstruct the mic.
Default values are currently based on Galaxy S7.
Created with Boxes.py (https://boxes.hackerspace-bamberg.de/) Command line: boxes PhoneHolder Command line short: boxes PhoneHolder
